{"tid":2206962,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"謝張繼聰搵到接班人啦","createTime":"2020-09-18T00:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T03:33:01.000Z","uid":220066,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"771ea87191fb2f68b4ff1391c98e641dd67c5411","tid":2206962,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T00:46:31.000Z","msg":"藝人袁偉豪（Ben）與張寶兒（Bowie）拍拖3年，今年五月二人聯名買樓共組愛巢。Ben今日在社交平台公布，原來去年今日（9月17日）已向女友張寶兒求婚成功，Ben在求婚一周年才公布喜訊。<br />\n<br />\n袁偉豪在IG發布影片，當日二人在加拿大尼亞加拉大瀑布做運動期間，Ben突然向Bowie單膝下跪，並送上戒指。<br />\n<br />\nBowie驚喜萬分，邊笑邊掩面流淚，Ben為女友拭淚，場面感人。最後Bowie伸手答應，二人互抱場面甜蜜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBen求婚成功，舉起V字手勢，盡顯興奮心情，Bowie又展示3卡鑽戒，片中主題曲還由Ben親自演唱，非常甜蜜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vsRBOif.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvsRBOif.png&h=ea21f22c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VXy1eYj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVXy1eYj.png&h=5c707322&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kSS9oRH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkSS9oRH.png&h=c174418d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d95538bd8f58a1f6ba63cf96e590220dc9c4f4c","tid":2206962,"uid":45182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T01:08:00.000Z","msg":"這麼醜的女。"},{"pid":"8ab1d6f2f89ecb10653f252ae3dbf5d3ebcfe1f5","tid":2206962,"uid":57462,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2d95538bd8f58a1f6ba63cf96e590220dc9c4f4c","tid":2206962,"uid":45182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T01:08:00.000Z","msg":"這麼醜的女。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T01:13:03.000Z","msg":"但係荷包腫漲呢..."},{"pid":"817b295a12f49f8588f5b61189f2d8502b94d131","tid":2206962,"uid":34466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T01:18:01.000Z","msg":"都好啊有人要咗佢<br />\n總要人犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dec27c65f9faed300dc6f22f8581256d4f13e41","tid":2206962